data.description: Wonderful 3BR, 2.5 BA home sitting on a little more than a half acre of land. With the newly renovated room this home has three bedrooms down plus an additional bedroom upstairs with a bonus room. The back yard is featured with an outside patio as well as having a screened in sitting area. The kitchen and great room area is ideal for entertaining and family time. Master bedroom has vaulted ceilings and huge walk-in closet. This home is a must see!!!
